*Probleme* su tamo gde počinje razmišljanje. (Problems are where thinking begins.)

Oni su se susreli sa mnogim *probleme*ma. (They encountered many problems.)

Taj čovek ne voli da se suočava sa svojim *probleme*ima. (That man doesn't like to face his problems.)

Ova vestica daje odgovore za sve *probleme*. (This witch gives answers to all problems.)

Oni su imali malo *problema* u svojoj vezi. (They had a few problems in their relationship.)